Text: I appreciate you forwarding this information to the appropriate people Now I really owe you lunch let me know when you are available Thanks Again Tom Clark office home email Tom Clark ResumeIIIdoc PGE Energy Trading and any other company referenced herein which uses the PGE name or logo are not the same company as Pacific Gas and Electric Company the California utility These companies are not regulated by the California Public Utilities Commission and customers do not have to buy products from these companies in order to continue to receive quality regulated services from the utility Tom Clark ResumeIIIdoc
